data.description: 4 Bedrooms/2 Baths.  Home has 3 Living areas -Formal LR and DR, Large den with built-ins & fireplace and a Spacious Sunroom off of den. Hardwood floors in living, dining rooms, den, 1 bedroom, and hall. Hard tile in kitchen, sunroom, laundry and bathrooms.  Galley style kitchen with ample counter and cabinet space.  Nice size Breakfast Room. Laundry room has built-in cabinets with access to the backyard. Great yard.  Attached storage room & detached building. Close to the Dalraida Shopping District, Gunter, Dalraida Commons, Dalraida Elementary School, I-65, and all parts of Montgomery.
